              "code": "\tlocation \u003d self.view.params.location\n\tbatteryID \u003d str(self.view.params.batteryID)\n\tvoltageTag \u003d system.tag.readBlocking(\u0027[default]Storage/\u0027 + location + \u0027/Battery \u0027 + batteryID + \u0027/Voltage\u0027)\n\tvoltage \u003d voltageTag[0].value\n\tvoltSPTag \u003d system.tag.readBlocking(\u0027[default]Storage/\u0027 + location + \u0027/Battery \u0027 + batteryID + \u0027/VoltageSP\u0027)\n\tvoltSP \u003d voltSPTag[0].value\n\tloadTag \u003d system.tag.readBlocking(\u0027[default]Storage/\u0027 + location + \u0027/Battery \u0027 + batteryID + \u0027/Load\u0027)\n\tload\u003d loadTag[0].value\n\tloadSPTag \u003d system.tag.readBlocking(\u0027[default]Storage/\u0027 + location + \u0027/Battery \u0027 + batteryID + \u0027/LoadSP\u0027)\n\tloadSP \u003d loadSPTag[0].value\n\tif voltage \u003e voltSP or load \u003e loadSP:\n\t\tvalue \u003d \u0027batteryCard batteryFault\u0027\n\telse:\n\t\tvalue \u003d \u0027batteryCard\u0027\n\treturn value",
              "type": "script"
